{"tid":676592,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人喺出面同喺屋企係兩個人？","createTime":"2018-05-24T13:23:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-12T12:50:16.000Z","uid":162406,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"e3df06e61cc7c24a86566ba5113b917e5c935a64","tid":676592,"uid":162406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T13:23:35.000Z","msg":"自己平時喺出面覺得算係自己最真嘅一面，尤其是同自己熟嗰啲朋友一齊，會發下癲講吓on9野咁。<br />\n但係一返到屋企 就唔會講嘢 唔會有任何表情，唔會想同屋企人講太多野，講多兩句就覺得佢哋好煩，我都唔知點解，總之就對屋企冇乜歸屬感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n自己其實好鍾意彈吉他同唱歌，但我喺佢哋面前真係會粒聲唔出，亦都唔想做任何野。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有冇人可以介紹啲地方，係唔會俾人聽到自己唱歌<br />\n同啲朋友一齊坐嘅時候唱我又冇所謂，但係冇理由要佢哋睇住我唱成晚㗎嘛，好冇空間好辛苦平時都係靠唱歌彈結他抒發下自己壓力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n救命 有冇咩好方法 認真求救<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79b8d68f443c2ebf32ffdccc5c3849222b8d561f","tid":676592,"uid":162406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T13:24:29.000Z","msg":"應該係話有咩好地方介紹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dec25615b4c9c95cb4c5c148d5b193ff9e527c24","tid":676592,"uid":162406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T13:26:52.000Z","msg":"有冇巴絲同我一樣，對住屋企人反而好內斂<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba7c76b84dfaf2a7f03f78af976c4eb7403f6adb","tid":676592,"uid":129506,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T13:32:27.000Z","msg":"應該好多人都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但其實係屋企先係最真，因為真正既我根本唔想曬心機曬時間扮多野講<br />\n<br />\n係出面就要揾野講扮有興趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"995c4d2529b0565b35833e9ebdfc66b32aaefd61","tid":676592,"uid":147847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T13:39:38.000Z","msg":"好正常姐 只不過係係屋企到冇人可以同你講啲on9野姐 而且又有代溝"},{"pid":"bdbf10251478bab91930bcc361e6cbe3ebfd0e9c","tid":676592,"uid":132587,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T13:42:02.000Z","msg":"屋企有人 屋企得自己一個 番工對上司 番工對同事 番工對客 對住女朋友<br />\n全部都可以有唔同人格<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1a476e9ca46fcf505d98586a495cda2993574b6","tid":676592,"uid":162406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ba7c76b84dfaf2a7f03f78af976c4eb7403f6adb","tid":676592,"uid":129506,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T13:32:27.000Z","msg":"應該好多人都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但其實係屋企先係最真，因為真正既我根本唔想曬心機曬時間扮多野講<br />\n<br />\n係出面就要揾野講扮有興趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T13:42:27.000Z","msg":"又唔係話扮有興趣，其實佢地喺屋企嘅時候，我都好想唱歌彈吉他發癲，不過就係因為佢哋喺度，所以我忍住<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db6f9e137ec8966e2202396c83c83f730ed421c6","tid":676592,"uid":162406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bdbf10251478bab91930bcc361e6cbe3ebfd0e9c","tid":676592,"uid":132587,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T13:42:02.000Z","msg":"屋企有人 屋企得自己一個 番工對上司 番工對同事 番工對客 對住女朋友<br />\n全部都可以有唔同人格<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T15:31:17.000Z","msg":"都係嘅 不過我對屋企嘅冷淡同平時嘅自己好大反差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0153f044854db9909a27b521bdbb488f6f2ee88","tid":676592,"uid":162406,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"995c4d2529b